Titolo: Gunnm: Martian Memory

Anno: 1998

Descrizione: Gunnm: Martian Memory (銃夢 ～火星の記憶～, Ganmu Kasei no Kioku) is a 1998 action role-playing video game for the PlayStation based on the Battle Angel Alita manga series.  To date it is the only Battle Angel Alita video game, and the only game developed by Yukito Products.  It has only been released in Japan.